            "answers": [
              {
                "text": "The appointment scheduling is terrible. I can never find available slots that work for me, and when I do find one, the system sometimes loses my selection when I go to confirm. Last month I thought I had booked an appointment but it never showed up on my calendar. Also, the mobile version of the site is nearly unusable — buttons are too small, text overlaps, and the calendar widget doesn't work properly on my phone."
              }
